content:
I guess….President Trump is not a fan of President Truman’s quote…”The buck stops here”. President Trump is still blaming via twitter the Obama administration for his hiring of National Security Adviser Michael Flynn. 
This despite the fact….Flynn was fired by Obama administration in 2014 and today CNN reports Pres. Obama warned Trump on hiring Flynn in their post-election meeting.

content:
Education Secretary Betsy DeVos’s budget cuts really should be getting your attention. Some fear it hurts working families, vulnerable children, and teachers.

To begin it calls for $ 9 billion in cuts or 13 percent, from the department.
It eliminates about $3.6 billion from programs earmarked for after-school programs and students who require special education 
The cuts could translate into 40 thousand teacher salaries to be slashed..

All while, investing a whopping $1.4 billion of new funding in “school choice”. An investment she says will grow to $20 billion annually.
